from typing import *
def f_gold(nums: List[int], goal: int) -> int:
    i1 = i2 = s1 = s2 = j = ans = 0
    n = len(nums)
    while j < n:
        s1 += nums[j]
        s2 += nums[j]
        while i1 <= j and s1 > goal:
            s1 -= nums[i1]
            i1 += 1
        while i2 <= j and s2 >= goal:
            s2 -= nums[i2]
            i2 += 1
        ans += i2 - i1
        j += 1
    return ans
